data.description: This home screams QUALITY!  Custom built with exceptional details! Private 3.5 acre lot surrounded by mature trees. Main level-3 beds/2 baths/3rd bedroom stubbed for ensuite.  Master suite connected to bonus room, perfect for a home office or nursery.  9' ceilings! Abundant natural light!  Terrace level w/ finished in-law suite, complete with full bath and private entry.  Tons of storage!  Dual paned thermal windows, brand new HVAC system, R19 insulation, copper plumbing, custom deck & more. Storage!! 48" acc doorways. Boat door too!  Must see to believe!
